description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 26, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 26, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 2 for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40261-42462-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [26 Votes, Common]
